data.title: Namibia: Ohorongo Cement plant nearing completion
data.meta_description: Company looking at exports to neighboring markets and even the Americas once plant comes online. Namibia based Ohorongo Cement is getting ready to inaugurate a cement unit in Otavi later this year, and plans to export cement to other countries once it comes online.
data.text: Company looking at exports to neighboring markets and even the Americas once plant comes online.
